Mmm...munch...yum...
Mo mo mo! Morimori declare Love
Raspberry is tastiest fruit in Iira!

rows.label: tlk70000044_01_msg0002
rows.name:
By the way, Morimori thank friends for
bringing many foods.

rows.label: tlk70000044_01_msg0003
rows.name:
By the way, is something happen?
Friends looking very small all of sudden
somehow.

rows.label: tlk70000044_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Mo-mo? It Morimori who get big?
Ohoho, friends have great humor sense!
Morimori almost buy it!

rows.label: tlk70000044_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Morimori learning all about cuisine of
Iira. Working very hard to sample
many dishes. Learning by eating!

rows.label: tlk70000044_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Favorite is Love Raspberry. So sweet!
So big! So plump! So juicy!

rows.label: tlk70000044_01_msg0007
rows.name:
Mo? If eat too many, Morimori get
even more biggerer? Ohoho, again with
the jokings!

rows.label: tlk70000044_01_msg0008
rows.name:
...Wait. Friends have serious faces.
Is possible friends actually concerned,
rather than teasing?

rows.label: tlk70000044_01_msg0009
rows.name:
Is very OK! No need for worries!
Morimori still growing so is needing
lots of nutrients. Is sign of good health!
